title: Louis van Gaal surprised by Manchester United's Premier League defeat to Arsenal - Halesowennews.co.uk
text:
Louis van Gaal was "amazed" by Manchester United's display as Arsenal got back to winning ways in some style. An air of positivity had been building around Old Trafford after a run of four straight wins in all competitions.
 Halesowennews.co.uk.
